From: YugabyteDB Voyager <amakala@yugabyte.com>
Subject: [YB-EXT] libpg_query toolchain fixes for portable regen

Adapts libpg_query's regen pipeline for use outside the maintainer's
macOS environment:
  - Makefile: respect LIBCLANG env var; use GNU sed -i; add regen_proto
    target and protoc-c include-path rewrite.
  - scripts/extract_source.rb: use modern ffi-clang predicate methods
    array? / pointer? instead of removed FFI::Clang::Types constants.

--- a/Makefile
+++ b/Makefile
@@ -113,7 +113,7 @@
